allegro: This drum, it's Breve's!
allegro: Breve was our drummer, and he was at the core of our success as a band. 
allegro: He was always making sure we kept good time, both when we were playing music and during our travels.
allegro: He must be around nearby! I'll bring this along, and return it to him when I see him.
allegro: It feels like I have an extra spring in my step when I play it. That might be useful while traversing this island.
do GameManager.dialogic_signal_end()